<a class="boxer" target="_blank" href="https://img.furusato-tax.jp/img/x/gcf/project/progresses/20200728/1_1fd45e5ec6f227579fdd24f20896b1cf5d834950.jpg"><img alt decoding="async" src="https://img.furusato-tax.jp/img/x/gcf/project/progresses/20200728/1_1fd45e5ec6f227579fdd24f20896b1cf5d834950.jpg" /></a>
